<h2 class="wikipedia">Wikipedia</h2>
<div class="wikipedia-extract-body wikipedia-extract-collapse"><p><b>Hurts</b> are an English synthpop duo formed in 2009, consisting of synthesist Adam Anderson and singer Theo Hutchcraft. Their first two albums, <i>Happiness</i> and <i>Exile</i>, both reached the top ten in the United Kingdom, Germany, Austria, Switzerland, Poland, and Finland.</p>
<p></p></div>
